wich puts your team in a pretty big disavantage.

I succesfully cloned a real §6Docm77§0 he is not as good as the original as he can't build or do any fancy things like that. all he can do is fight the other teams with you.

Sadly the cloning comes with a downside, he lost his skills to build things, craft things and even mine things, all he can do is fight.

Sadly i was unable to give him some weapons and armor so this will be up to you to give it.
Sadly i can't let you choose wich armor he gets as the cloning process was highly unstable and he can only wear specific armor and only use one specific weapon, i am sorry about this.
But hey one extra teammember is better than none right?
